Constructor Detail

RadioButtonComponent

public RadioButtonComponent(Element radioButtonElement,
                            RadioButtonGroup radioButtonGroup)
Creates a RadioButtonComponent from the specified radioButton Element and the specified List of other radio button components in the same radiobutton group. /

Parameters:
radioButtonGroup - a RadioButtonGroup container, which contains all other RadioButtonComponents in the form that belong to the same radio button group (ie, have the same name); this parameter can be null, which denotes that this component has no name attribute, and therefore no associated radiobutton group.
